reviews.review_text: Weekend at the Beach!!! Saturday afternoon with the Grateful Dead!  From start to finish, this was one amazing show.  The Shakedown Street was the opener of a barn-burner of a second set.  As I was part of this show, I can remember how the clouds hung right over the Ventura Fairgrounds.  Let's just say that the experience was comic!
